                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9671" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2415</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">808 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“数字”生渭水，“智造”满长安：三友集团的数智化转型之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digitalization and Intelligence Bring Intelligent Manufacturing：The Number Intelligent Transformation Road of Sanyou Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘海鸥，田颖暄，王海英，李文福</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">燕山大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐山三友集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化；高端•智能•绿色•安全；转型路径；新质生产力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital and intelligent; High-end, smart, green and safe; Transformation path; New quality productivity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在技术革命性变革和生产要素创新性配置的双重驱动下，传统制造业的高端化、智能化、绿色化转型已成为培育新质生产力的关键路径。三友集团立足产业深度转型升级，以数智化与绿色化转型为双轮驱动，通过创新体制机制、优化资源配置、强化技术攻关等实招硬招，全力培育新质生产力，为传统制造业高质量发展注入新动能。案例聚焦传统制造业大型国有企业唐山三友集团的数智化转型实践，以“智慧三友”数智化建设为切入点，深入剖析其转型前的行业痛点、转型中的关键矛盾及破解路径，并评估转型成效，为大型国企的数智化升级提供可借鉴的实践样本。案例旨在引导学习者探究国有企业如何以数智化转型驱动高端化、智能化、绿色化与安全生产协同发展，在具体实践中感知新质生产力的培育逻辑；同时，启发学习者从国家战略与可持续发展的高度审视国企转型，培养其全局思维与长远发展意识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">TDriven by both revolutionary technological changes and innovative allocation of production factors, the high-end, intelligent and green transformation of traditional manufacturing industries has become a key path to cultivating new quality productive forces. Sanyou Group, based on the in-depth transformation and upgrading of its industries, takes digital intelligence and green transformation as the dual drivers. Through practical and effective measures such as innovating systems and mechanisms, optimizing resource allocation, and strengthening technological research and development, it is fully committed to cultivating new quality productivity and injecting new impetus into the high-quality development of traditional manufacturing. The case focuses on the digital and intelligent transformation practice of Tangshan Sanyou Group, a large state-owned enterprise in traditional manufacturing. Taking the construction of &quot;Smart Sanyou&quot; as the entry point, it systematically reviews its transformation process, deeply analyzes the industry pain points before the transformation, the key contradictions during the transformation and the solutions, and assesses the transformation achievements, providing a practical sample for the digital and intelligent upgrade of large state-owned enterprises. This case aims to guide learners to explore how state-owned enterprises can drive the coordinated development of high-end, intelligent, green and safe production through digital and intelligent transformation, and perceive the logic of cultivating new quality productivity in specific practice. Meanwhile, the case is based on the perspective of the development of The Times, inspiring learners to examine the transformation of state-owned enterprises from the height of national strategy and sustainable development, and cultivating their overall thinking and long-term development awareness.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数智化转型的概念及动因；数智化转型的瓶颈(瓶颈理论)；数字化三阶段理论；数字资源编排</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
